Directed By Brandon Cronenberg.

Written By Brandon Cronenberg.

Cast Alexander Skarsgård .Mia Goth .Cleopatra Coleman.

Language English.

Producer Michael Bloom. Ryan Bobkin. Andrew Cividino. Rob Cotterill. Brandon Cronenberg. Jeff Deutchman. Brendan Gunn. Jonathan Halperyn. Karen Harnisch. Ryan Heller. Karim Hussain. Anita Juka. Ivona Juka. Daniel
Kresmery. Emily Kulasa. Adrian Love. Laurie May. Charlotte Mickie. Lajos Nagy. Hengameh Panahi. Christina Piovesan.

Production Film Forge. Hero Squared. 4 Film.
